NK040(thi)042:1: // phag mo khros ma'i bskang ba bzhugs so //
NK040(thi)042:3: stong nyid chos kyi dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK040(thi)042:4: thugs rje'i sprul pa bdag gzhan gnyis kyi dpal //
NK040(thi)042:5: rnam par thar pa gsum gyi sgo 'byed ma //
NK040(thi)042:6: shes rab pha rol phyin ma'i thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)042:7: rtog med sgeg pa'i tshul gyi sku sprul pa //
NK040(thi)042:8: nag mo khros mas lha rnams zil gyis gnon //
NK040(thi)042:9: chos nyid mi 'gyur sku mdog mthing nag ma //
NK040(thi)042:10: ma longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yi thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)042:12: g.yas nas gcod byed gri gug bsnams pa yi //
NK040(thi)042:13: bdud dang gti mug tshogs rnams bsreg par byed //
NK040(thi)042:14: nyon mongs rnam rtog thams cad rtsad nas gcod //
NK040(thi)042:15: phrin las mthar phyin ma yis thugs dam g.yon pas thod pa khrag gi gang ba bsnams //
NK040(thi)042:16: thugs rje'i khyab pa'i tshul gyi 'gro don mdzad //
NK040(thi)042:17: stong nyid thugs rje'i 'brel ba'i bdag nyid can //
NK040(thi)042:18: thugs rje'i 'gro don mdzad ma khyod kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)042:20: phyag mtshan kha t+w+aam ga ni thugs kar 'dzin //
NK040(thi)042:21: dug gsum rtsad gcod 'khor ba'i g.yul ngo sel //
NK040(thi)042:22: sku gsung thugs dang mnyam sbyor khro mo'i sku //
NK040(thi)042:23: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa'i thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)042:24: srid gsum rnam rtog thams cad 'jom pa'i phyir //
NK040(thi)042:25: 'jig byed chen mo phag gi gdong pa can //
NK040(thi)042:26: me dpung klong na bzhugs pa'i khro gnyer can //
NK040(thi)042:27: mthu stobs bdag mo khyod kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)042:28: za byed chen po gdug pa'i mche ba can //
NK040(thi)042:29: log 'dren thams cad zil gyis gnon mdzad pa //
NK040(thi)042:30: zhal gdangs ljag rkyang mkha' la rab tu spyod //
NK040(thi)042:31: stong gsum sgra sgrog khyod kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)042:32: srid gsum 'thor byed spyan gsum me 'od 'phro //
NK040(thi)042:33: ye shes lnga ldan dbu la thod pas brgyan //
NK040(thi)042:34: sku lnga rab rdzogs ye shes mkha' 'gro ma //
NK040(thi)042:35: yon tan rdzogs phyir dur khrod rgyan gyis brgyan //
NK040(thi)042:36: yon tan mthar phyin khyod kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)042:37: ngo mtshar chen po dgyes pa'i gad rgyang can //
NK040(thi)042:38: bzhad pa'i gad mos 'khor ba thar par 'dren //
NK040(thi)042:39: khros pa'i gad mos dgra bgegs brlag par byed //
NK040(thi)042:40: gdug pa brlag mdzad khyod kyis thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)042:41: zhe sdang 'joms mdzad sbrul gyi zhag pa can //
NK040(thi)042:42: nga rgyal 'jom mdzad stag gi sham thab can //
NK040(thi)042:43: 'byung po tshar gcod thod pa'i phreng bas brgyan //
NK040(thi)042:44: rtags kyi 'gro don mdzad pa'i thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)042:45: bcom ldan khros ma nag mo'i thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)042:46: chos sku 'gags med rtags su phag gi dbu //
NK040(thi)042:47: phag skad drag po steng du sgra sgrog pa'i //
NK040(thi)042:48: gzugs med khams gsum ma lus dbang du sdud //
NK040(thi)042:49: bskang ngo khyed kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)042:50: bcom ldan khros ma nag mo'i phag skad drag po bar du sgrog pa yis //
NK040(thi)042:51: gzugs khams thams cad ma lus dbang du gzugs khams 'dul mdzad phag gi dbu //
NK040(thi)042:52: bskang ngo khyed kyi thugs bcom ldan khros ma nag mo'i phag skad 'og tu sgrog pa yi //
NK040(thi)042:53: 'dod khams thams cad dbang du bsdus //
NK040(thi)042:55: bskang ngo khyed kyi thugs bcom ldan rdo rje phag mo'i phag skad shar du sgrogs pa yi //
NK040(thi)042:57: shar phyogs brgya byin rdul du barloga /
NK040(thi)042:58: brgya byin 'dul mdzad phag gi dbu //
NK040(thi)042:59: bskang ngo khyed kyi thugs bcom ldan rdo rje phag mo'i thugs phag skad lho ru sgrog pa yi //
NK040(thi)042:61: lho phyogs gshin rje rdul du gshin rje 'dul mdzad phag gi dbu //
NK040(thi)042:62: bskang ngo khyed kyi bcom ldan rdo rje phag mo'i phag skad nub tu sgrogs pa yis //
NK040(thi)042:64: nub phyogs klu gdon rdul du klu gdon 'dul mdzad phag gi dbu //
NK040(thi)042:65: bskang ngo khyed kyi bcom ldan rdo rje phag mo'i phag skad byang du sgrogs pa yi //
NK040(thi)042:67: byang phyogs gnod sbyin rdul gnod sbyin 'dul mdzad phag gi dbu //
NK040(thi)042:68: bskang ngo khyed kyi bcom ldan rdo rje phag mo'i phag skad shar lhor sgrog pa yi //
NK040(thi)042:70: shar lho me lha rdul me lha 'dul mdzad phag
NK040(thi)042:71: gi bskang ngo khyed kyi bcom ldan rdo rje phag
NK040(thi)042:72: mo'i phag skad lho nub sgrogs pa yi //
NK040(thi)042:74: lho nub srin po rdul srin po 'dul mdzad phag gi dbu //
NK040(thi)042:75: bskang ngo khyed kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)042:76: bcom ldan rdo rje phag skad nub byang sgrogs pa yi //
NK040(thi)042:78: nub byang rlung lha rdul du rlung lha 'dul mdzad phag gi dbu //
NK040(thi)042:79: bskang ngo khyed kyi thugs dam bcom ldan phag skad byang shar sgrogs pa yi //
NK040(thi)042:81: byang shar 'byung po rdul 'byung po 'dul mdzad phag
NK040(thi)042:82: gi bskang ngo khyed kyi thugs bcom ldan phag skad
NK040(thi)042:85: steng gi tshangs pa rdul du tshangs pa 'dul mdzad phag gi dbu //
NK040(thi)042:86: bskang ngo khyed kyi bcom ldan rdo rje phag skad 'og tu sgrogs pa yi //
NK040(thi)042:88: 'og gi sa bdag rdul sa bdag 'dul mdzad phag gi dbu //
NK040(thi)042:89: bskang ngo khyed kyi thugs srid gsum thams cad zil gyis gnon //
NK040(thi)042:90: 'khor du ma gyur gang yang med //
NK040(thi)042:91: khams gsum 'dul mdzad khros ma yi //
NK040(thi)042:92: bskang ngo khyed kyi bcom ldan rdo rje phag mo'i khams gsum thams cad khyod kyi zas //
NK040(thi)042:93: zas su ma gyur gang yang med //
NK040(thi)042:94: khams gsum 'dul mdzad khros ma yi //
NK040(thi)042:95: bskang ngo khyed kyi bcom ldan rdo rje phag mo'i thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)042:96: 'dod khams thams cad khyod kyi zas //
NK040(thi)042:97: bde ba chen po'i ngang du bzhes //
NK040(thi)042:99: bde chen khros ma'i thugs bskang ngo khyed kyi bcom ldan rdo rje phag mo yi //
NK040(thi)042:100: zhe sdang thams cad khyod kyi zas //
NK040(thi)042:101: skye ba med pa'i mchod pa bzhes //
NK040(thi)042:102: zhe sdang 'dul byed khros ma yi //
NK040(thi)042:103: skye med khros ma'i bskang ngo bskal pa'i bcom ldan rdo rje phag mo yi //
NK040(thi)042:104: nga rgyal thams cad khyod kyi zas //
NK040(thi)042:105: mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang du bzhes //
NK040(thi)042:106: nga rgyal 'dul mdzad khros ma yi //
NK040(thi)042:107: mnyam nyid mkha' bskang ngo khyed kyi thugs bcom ldan rdo rje phag mo yi //
NK040(thi)042:108: phrag dog thams cad khyod kyi zas //
NK040(thi)042:109: rang byung chen po'i ngang du bzhes //
NK040(thi)042:110: phrag dog 'dul mdzad khros ma yi //
NK040(thi)042:111: rang byung khros ma'i bskang ngo khyed kyi bcom ldan rdo rje phag mo yi //
NK040(thi)042:112: gti mug thams cad khyod kyi zas //
NK040(thi)042:113: chos sku chen po'i ngang du bzhes //
NK040(thi)042:114: gti mug 'dul mdzad khros ma yi //
NK040(thi)042:115: chos sku khros ma'i bskang ngo khyed kyi bcom ldan rdo rje phag mo yi //
NK040(thi)042:116: klu gnyen sa bdag khyod kyi zas //
NK040(thi)042:117: klu gnyen sa bdag 'dul mdzad khros ma yi //
NK040(thi)042:118: bskang ngo khyed kyi bcom ldan rdo rje phag mo yi //
NK040(thi)042:119: btsan dang 'gong po khyod kyi zas //
NK040(thi)042:120: btsan dang 'gong po 'dul mdzad khros ma yi //
NK040(thi)042:121: bskang ngo khyed kyi bcom ldan rdo rje phag mo yi //
NK040(thi)042:122: bdud dang rgyal po khyod kyi zas //
NK040(thi)042:123: bdud dang rgyal po 'dul mdzad khros ma yi //
NK040(thi)042:124: bskang ngo khyed kyi bcom ldan rdo rje phag mo yi //
NK040(thi)042:125: dkor bdag dam sri khyod kyi zas //
NK040(thi)042:126: dam sri 'dul mdzad khros ma yi //
NK040(thi)042:127: bskang ngo khyed kyi bcom ldan rdo rje phag mo yi //
NK040(thi)042:128: bdud po yi dwags 'dul mdzad khros ma yi //
NK040(thi)042:129: bskang ngo khyed kyi bcom ldan rdo rje phag mo yi //
NK040(thi)042:130: thugs dam bskang gyur dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK040(thi)042:131: rnal 'byor bcol pa'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
